                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t16890516-98-off427 t16890516-98-cd428"></join> last, stealing a pair of Cloth Breeches trim'd with Gold value 20 s. a Peruke 18 s. a Stuff Riding Hood 20 s. 4 Pewter Dishes 12 s. and divers other Goods, all to the value of about 15 l. &amp;c.
            </rs> The Peruke and the Breeches were found upon him. And altho he denied it upon his Tryal the Jury found him <rs id="t16890516-98-verdict429" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t16890516-98-verdict429" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               guilty
            </rs> of Felony and Burglary.</p>
